<item>
            <title>[LU-188] Reduce startup messages </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-188</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Making Lustre start up messages more brief. For example, Perhaps the typical three lines of:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lustre: OBD class driver, info@clusterfs.com&lt;br/&gt;
        Lustre Version: 1.6.5&lt;br/&gt;
        Build Version: 1.6.5-2.1.29HD-rsrel-RB-2.1-13122-2008-08-20-19:05&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;could be compressed down on to one line.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
